p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;This work is dedicated to &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; font-weight:696; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;José Rizal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;, whose vision, intellect, and sacrifice continue to light the way for Filipinos everywhere. From his early years in &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; font-weight:696; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Calamba&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt; to his final moments in &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; font-weight:696; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Bagumbayan&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;, Rizal exemplified the power of knowledge, justice, and a deep love for his country.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
