&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;This is also dedicated to the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; font-weight:696; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Filipino youth&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:14pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;, the future of the nation, whose passion and potential carry forward Rizal's dream of a just, free, and prosperous Philippines. May his courage inspire you to embrace education, stand for what is right, and honor the sacrifices made for the freedom we enjoy today. The legacy of Rizal lives on in your hands.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
